Project 3: Application drawing geometric figures 
individual 

1) Compile (10%) 

2) Using a TabViewController (10%) 

3) Tab1 = specifications of the figure (40%) 
Figure: Square, triangle, circle 
Background color 
fill Color 
Color Edge 

Selection can be Button, Radio Group or segmented cell (see) 

4) Tab2: Draw figure with specifications (20%) 

5) Gesture, pinch in the figure, rises and falls. (20%)
